@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jedpvx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v0 = 0.94
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.83) - tmp) * ((tmp + 0.76 - v1 + 0.29) + wp.abs(tmp + 0.16)))
    v0 = 0.12
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.27)))
    tmp = ((tmp + v0) - wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.33)))
    data[tid] = v0
